data.description: Near the Edom, TX Arts District is this secluded 4.45 mol acres. Property is partially fenced, sits back off the road, has a pond, trees and pasture. Spacious 2BR, 1BA Home. Huge great room with WB stove. Open kitchen and dining. New Carpet early 2016. Nice covered porch. 30X40 shop with electricity and concrete floor. 10X40 Storage Bldg. 18X80 Manufactured home that is being used for storage. Could be remodeled for second home on property.
